enhanced_by.reason: The method 'lockedProductPosition' provides the current position which is necessary to determine if auto-subscribe should be set.
Checking the personal left quota is important to ensure the user has the necessary quota before setting auto-subscribe.
Both methods involve subscription actions and can share similar assertions regarding subscription status.
The method 'lockedSubscriptionRecord' provides historical subscription data which can be used to verify the success of the auto-subscribe operation.
